des:
Welcome to Approximationaism as an Art Therapy, by Vayu Vaidya. In this skill, consisting of mindful meditation on Godel's ontological proof and a review of a publication by the author, we explore a system of meditation in the present on a mathematical truth and the closure of the proof in Gestalt.
At any point in the skill you can say "start over" to start over, "stop" to exit the skill and "help" for help.
